1. *Zver* je istrčala iz šume. (The *beast* ran out of the forest.)
2. Lovac je upucao *zver*. (*The beast* was shot by the hunter.)
3. U narodnim pričama, *zveri* su često simbol zla. (In folk tales, *beasts* are often a symbol of evil.)
4. Ova oblast je dom za mnoge vrste *zveri*. (This area is home to many species of *wild animals*.)
5. Njegova ljubav prema motociklima je prava *zver*. (His love for motorcycles is a real *passion*.)
6. Neke biljke su *zveri* u smislu da su sposobne da rastu u ekstremnim uslovima. (Some plants are *beasts* in the sense that they are capable of growing in extreme conditions.)
7. *Zverinjak* u zoološkom vrtu je popularno mesto za posetu. (The *zoo enclosure* is a popular place to visit in the zoo.)
8. Vojska je koristila *zveri* kao oružje tokom rata. (The army used *beasts* as weapons during the war.)
9. Njen glas ima snagu prave *zveri*. (Her voice has the power of a true *beast*.)
10. Ukoliko želite da preživite u divljini, morate biti spremni da se borite kao prava *zver*. (If you want to survive in the wilderness, you must be prepared to fight like a real *beast*.)